This paper focuses on data management in IoT, which is a subfield of computer networking and communication (cs.NI). It also discusses pricing strategies, which can be related to computer engineering (cs.CE) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions security and privacy concerns, which fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the use of intelligent and adaptive mechanisms can be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
